    <description>This package provides support for adding features to the Sandcastle Help File Builder project. In particular, the tools enable what follows.
* Adding LaTeX content to SHFB documentation files.
* Managing images in SHFB Reference topics. 
* Setting lists of keywords to be colorized in code examples.
